#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn8.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn8.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 8 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 8 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Vaṅgīsavagga "
msgstr "1. With Vaṅgīsa "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn8.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Ānandasutta "
msgstr "4. With Ānanda "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.405, sc1
msgctxt "sn8.4:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ānando sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time Venerable Ānanda was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.4:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya sāvatthiṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi āyasmatā vaṅgīsena pacchāsamaṇena. "
msgstr "Then Venerable Ānanda robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and robe, entered Sāvatthī for alms with Venerable Vaṅgīsa as his second monk. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.4:1.3"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmato vaṅgīsassa anabhirati uppannā hoti, rāgo cittaṃ anuddhaṃseti. "
msgstr "And at that time Venerable Vaṅgīsa became dissatisfied, as lust infected his mind. "

msgctxt "sn8.4:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then he addressed Ānanda in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn8.4:2.1"
msgid "“Kāmarāgena ḍayhāmi, "
msgstr "“I’ve got a burning desire for pleasure; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:2.2"
msgid "cittaṃ me pariḍayhati; "
msgstr "My mind is on fire! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:2.3"
msgid "Sādhu nibbāpanaṃ brūhi, "
msgstr "Please, out of compassion, Gotama, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:2.4"
msgid "anukampāya gotamā”ti. "
msgstr "tell me how to quench the flames.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn8.4:3.1"
msgid "“Saññāya vipariyesā, "
msgstr "“Your mind is on fire "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:3.2"
msgid "cittaṃ te pariḍayhati; "
msgstr "because of a perversion of perception. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:3.3"
msgid "Nimittaṃ parivajjehi, "
msgstr "Turn away from the feature of things "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:3.4"
msgid "subhaṃ rāgūpasaṃhitaṃ. "
msgstr "that’s attractive, provoking lust. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn8.4:4.1"
msgid "Saṅkhāre parato passa, "
msgstr "See all conditioned phenomena as other, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:4.2"
msgid "dukkhato mā ca attato; "
msgstr "as suffering and not-self. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:4.3"
msgid "Nibbāpehi mahārāgaṃ, "
msgstr "Extinguish the great fire of lust, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:4.4"
msgid "mā ḍayhittho punappunaṃ. "
msgstr "don’t burn up again and again. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.406, sc5
msgctxt "sn8.4:5.1"
msgid "Asubhāya cittaṃ bhāvehi, "
msgstr "With mind unified and serene, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:5.2"
msgid "ekaggaṃ susamāhitaṃ; "
msgstr "meditate on the ugly aspects of the body. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:5.3"
msgid "Sati kāyagatā tyatthu, "
msgstr "With mindfulness immersed in the body, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:5.4"
msgid "nibbidābahulo bhava. "
msgstr "be full of disillusionment. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn8.4:6.1"
msgid "Animittañca bhāvehi, "
msgstr "Meditate on the signless, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:6.2"
msgid "mānānusayamujjaha; "
msgstr "give up the underlying tendency to conceit; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:6.3"
msgid "Tato mānābhisamayā, "
msgstr "and when you comprehend conceit, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.4:6.4"
msgid "upasanto carissasī”ti. "
msgstr "you will live at peace.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
